Part1
=====
Created joi 29 ianuarie 2015

Drivers and busses
* There are controllers!
	* bus drivers
	* device drivers
* Drivers have two parts
	* device-specific
	* OS-specific
* Drivers can be splited in:
	* Packet-oriented
	* Block-oriented
	* Byte-oriented	
* An OS performs 5 management fct:
	* CPU/process
	* memory
	* network
	* storage
	* device I/O
* Device Driver → drives a device
* Driver → drives just another piece of software
